20
00:01:03,392 --> 00:01:09,952
=The Empress Dowager On A Second Spring=

21
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:18,218
(Half a day earlier)

22
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:18,920
Your Majesty.

23
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,359
The Empress Dowager deceived me.

24
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:31,616
This matter

25
00:01:31,616 --> 00:01:32,959
reached your ears so soon?

26
00:01:33,536 --> 00:01:34,200
It appears

27
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,640
the one behind it
orchestrated this deliberately.

28
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:38,519
To let me know
about the prince's lineage.

29
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:39,400
What's wrong with it?

30
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,760
The truth of his lineage is important.

31
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,359
But if his true aim

32
00:01:44,719 --> 00:01:45,959
is to make you have no heir?

33
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:48,920
You harbor doubts

34
00:01:49,239 --> 00:01:51,439
about Noble Lady Zhu
being the prince's mother,

35
00:01:51,712 --> 00:01:53,120
but once officially acknowledged,

36
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,560
no one may question it.

37
00:01:54,848 --> 00:01:56,879
Now, they challenge
the prince's lineage.

38
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:57,840
In the future,

39
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,000
they'll challenge your lineage.

40
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:02,000
That is the true danger.

41
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,919
Found the rumor's origin?

42
00:02:10,912 --> 00:02:11,800
Your Majesty,

43
00:02:11,904 --> 00:02:14,599
it originated
from Noble Lady Zhu's palace.

44
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,199
They planted agents

45
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,199
in her chambers!

46
00:02:18,039 --> 00:02:19,759
How thorough of my uncle.

47
00:02:20,039 --> 00:02:20,960
The solution is simple.

48
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:22,800
Explain.

49
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,520
Rather than let others verify it,

50
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,319
we should strike first.

51
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:28,159
You should personally verify it.

52
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:31,800
If Noble Lady Zhu remains a virgin,

53
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:33,800
it proves treasonous deception.

54
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:36,000
Concealing the prince's true parentage

55
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:37,759
would then become impossible.

56
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:40,520
But favoring her...

57
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,159
Since they crave a spectacle,

58
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:44,599
we'll give them a performance.

59
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,360
An excellent strategy.

60
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,240
(Xuanming Palace)

61
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:01,319
The Office of Imperial Affairs
awaits your selection.

62
00:03:01,919 --> 00:03:03,199
Noble Lady Zhu serves me well.

63
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,639
She entered my harem,

64
00:03:04,879 --> 00:03:05,919
but I've yet to visit her.

65
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,199
Perhaps

66
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,560
I shall visit Noble Lady Zhu tonight.

67
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:13,919
Your Majesty.

68
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:15,560
