70
00:03:37,952 --> 00:03:41,825
=Episode 7=

71
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,759
Your Majesty.

72
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:46,080
After examination,

73
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:49,439
