isn't currently menstruating.

74
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:53,719
She has never borne children

75
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,240
and remains a virgin.

76
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,719
Noble Lady Zhu is the prince's mother.

77
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,919
How could she retain her virginity?

78
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,439
If others ask this,

79
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:09,240
how will you respond?

80
00:04:10,719 --> 00:04:13,240
We'll respond exactly

81
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,520
as you instruct, Your Majesty.

82
00:04:15,552 --> 00:04:18,399
We follow
your command, Your Majesty.

83
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:25,040
Your Ladyship,

84
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,720
you impersonated the prince's mother

85
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,160
and deceived the Emperor.

86
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:32,480
You've committed
multiple capital offenses.

87
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:34,079
It's...

88
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:37,439
The Empress Dowager
ordered me to pose as his mother.

89
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,680
I fully confess my crime.

90
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,920
I beg Your Majesty's mercy.

91
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,959
Her Majesty arranged this deception.

92
00:04:42,639 --> 00:04:43,439
So you know

93
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:44,800
the child's mother, right?

94
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,720
Her Majesty

95
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,560
never told me about that.

96
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,040
I truly have no knowledge.

97
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:50,839
Someone!

98
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,480
Take her out and execute her.

99
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,240
Yes.

100
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:53,879
Alright!

101
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,199
I'll tell you!

102
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:55,959
Your Majesty!

103
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,040
I'll confess!

104
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:59,120
I'll confess!

105
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,839
I knew you wouldn't be asleep

106
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,720
on such a beautiful night.

107
00:05:14,199 --> 00:05:16,920
What brings you here at this hour?

108
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,800
Our last moon-viewing was cut short.

109
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:20,879
Tonight's moon shines brilliantly.

110
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:23,279
I invite you to share
this spectacle with me

111
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:28,000
