132
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,920
We must investigate thoroughly.

133
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:35,639
Fuji.

134
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,319
We're going to Yixiang Palace.

135
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:38,600
Watch Noble Lady Zhu.

136
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,959
No one shall enter

137
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,240
without my permission.

138
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:43,240
Yes.

139
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:53,480
As you said, these are just rumors.

140
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:56,639
