152
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,519
Zhao Chengtian!

153
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,639
What are you doing?

154
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,000
I shall eliminate him

155
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:35,160
to protect the purity
of the royal bloodline.

156
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,839
Didn't you come to watch the moon?

157
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,000
To watch the moon

158
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,759
and certain people.

159
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:50,519
His Majesty arrives!

160
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:00,560
Why are you here at this hour?

161
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,040
Is anything wrong?

162
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,120
Recent rumors in the palace

163
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,600
doubt the prince's origins.

164
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,040
I fear such gossip spreading

165
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,240
would tarnish our reputation,

166
00:08:10,759 --> 00:08:12,519
so I came to discuss with Her Majesty

167
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,480
and, additionally, to verify

168
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:17,560
whether this child
is truly yours, Your Majesty.

169
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,079
Uncle, you're kidding.

170
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,120
Xiao Hu is unquestionably my son.

171
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,959
As you noted earlier,

172
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,399
