173
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,639
Since they're rumors,

174
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,960
why care about them?

175
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,639
For our family's reputation,

176
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:36,399
could you please trace

177
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:38,240
the source of these falsehoods?

178
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:41,120
That such slander spreads
unchecked through the palace

179
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:43,519
