investigate these rumors

182
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,879
to restore order to the court.

183
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,039
Precisely.

184
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,200
Such defamatory talk

185
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:55,399
